
Many businesses have evolved into ditigal firms to become more competitive and efficient. 

Zheng, Yajun. (2024). Do Information Systems Today Play a Strategic Role in Business?. Journal of Soft Computing and Decision Analytics. 2. 65-70. 10.31181/jscda21202432. 


The company has a challenge (new technology and competition) --> 
Everyone works together (Management - strategy and select technology, Organization - revise functions and processes, Technology - devices) --> 
Information System (made, tested, used) --> 
company solution (growth in sales, service, and operations)  
